<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="7Dec1938"><font color="red">7 December 1938</font> <i>NLVP</i> (from Ben Huebsch to Paul L&eacute;on): ABSENCE REPLY LETTER SEPTEMBER 20 IMPEDES PUBLICATION BECAUSE PAPER LIMITED EDITION CANNOT BE ORDERED UNTIL WE TELL FABER QUANTITY REQUIRED STOP SIMULTANEOUS ESSENTIAL TO COPYRIGHT THEREFORE DELAY INTERFERES BOTH EDITIONS STOP PLEASE ANSWER EXPLICITLY IMMEDIATELY </div>
